{"tid":1106342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有冇巴打有驗眼好介紹?","createTime":"2019-04-14T13:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T09:54:03.000Z","uid":211322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1654601b1661442286762f07c5d540ddd76143a","tid":1106342,"uid":211322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"近依一年隻眼睇嘢好似 越嚟越矇上次驗眼係1年前，去普通眼鏡鋪正係驗度數，職員同我講散光深咗幾十咁樣，但我依一年發覺睇嘢好似集中唔到，冇咩力，隻眼成日好累，望有光晚嘢有啲辛苦，散光應該再深咗好多，我有每日望同一個地方既 習慣，1年前唔帶眼鏡可以望到果個地方既文字，到依家已經完全望唔到散哂咁一pat嘢。<br />\n想認認真真驗一次眼睇下會唔會有隱性眼疾病果啲。有冇巴打有好地方介紹，價錢不是問題。<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8391a81ef18d4d6bbf9a9c351b70699598aee1","tid":1106342,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"27850649053e41bd2c22385976488bf0d47157f6","tid":1106342,"uid":211322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d184dad700e9cba4c14a3f5d8d6525f27fdf62b","tid":1106342,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"驗左存"},{"pid":"c9d46c50d014e3ecba2a57fb6265f065466646cf","tid":1106342,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d184dad700e9cba4c14a3f5d8d6525f27fdf62b","tid":1106342,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"驗左存"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:28:25.000Z","msg":"驗左未 邊間 搵緊"},{"pid":"bf58f8054718aade022c7d5feef4ee2509725fe0","tid":1106342,"uid":211322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9d46c50d014e3ecba2a57fb6265f065466646cf","tid":1106342,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d184dad700e9cba4c14a3f5d8d6525f27fdf62b","tid":1106342,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2